1️⃣ Detailed Screen Specification

Atlas by Vektra — Matchup Projection Screen (v7 Canonical)
Theme: Deep Graphite Institutional

A. Purpose

    This screen provides:

    Model-based win probability

    Implied fair moneyline (American odds)

    Structural signals explaining projection

    Historical head-to-head ledger

    It is clinical, quantitative, and neutral.

    No motivational language. No gamification.

